</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">Page1</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Page</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">form_model</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="sh">'</span><span class="s">player</span><span class="sh">'</span>
    <span class="n">form_fields</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="sh">'</span><span class="s">contribution</span><span class="sh">'</span><span class="p">]</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></figure> <ul> <li> <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Page2(WaitPage)</code>：全員揃うまで待つページ＋同期処理</p> <ul> <li> <p>WaitPage は 同じグループの全員が到達するまで待機させます。</p> </li> <li> <p>全員が到達した瞬間に、after_all_players_arrive が 1回だけ呼ばれます。</p> </li> <li> <p>定義した compute 関数で集計を行います。</p> </li> </ul> </li> </ul> <figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-python" data-lang="python"><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
2
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="k">class</span> <span class="nc">Page2</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">WaitPage</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">after_all_players_arrive</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">compute</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></figure> <ul> <li><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Page3(Page)</code>：結果表示ページ</li> </ul> <figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-python" data-lang="python"><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
